  "prompt": "How do you play the game Snaps?",
  "response": "\"Snaps\" is a fun, interactive guessing game that involves both verbal and non-verbal cues. The objective is to guess a secret word or phrase based on the clues provided by the \"snapper.\" Here\u2019s how to play:\n\n### Basic Rules:\n1. **Choose the Snapper**: One player is the \"snapper\" who knows the secret word or phrase.\n2. **Secret Word/Phrase**: The snapper selects a word or phrase (often a common noun or a well-known phrase).\n3. **Clue Structure**:\n   - **Consonants**: For consonants, the snapper says \"Snap\" followed by a number of snaps (claps). Each snap corresponds to a letter in the alphabet. For example, \"Snap, Snap, snap\" would indicate the letter \"C\" (the third letter of the alphabet).\n   - **Vowels**: For vowels, the snapper says \"Snap\" and then says the vowel (e.g., \"Snap, A\" for the letter \"A\").\n4. **Word Length**: The snapper can give hints about the length of the word or phrase by stating it or using gestures.\n5. **Guessing**: The other players listen to the snaps and try to guess the hidden word or phrase based on the clues.\n\n### Example:\n- **Secret Word**: \"Apple\"\n- **Clues**:\n  - \"Snap, A\" (hinting at the letter \"A\")\n  - \"Snap, snap, snap, snap, snap\" (indicating the letter \"P\")\n  - \"Snap, P\" (hinting at the letter \"P\")\n  - \"Snap, L\" (hinting at the letter \"L\")\n- Players piece together the clues to guess \"Apple.\"\n\n### Tips:\n- **Practice**: The snapper should practice snapping clearly and consistently.\n- **Start Simple**: Begin with short, common words to make it easier for everyone to understand the rules.\n- **Be Patient**: Give players time to decode the snaps and make their guesses.\n\n### Variations:\n- **Themed Snaps**: Choose words or phrases from a specific category, like movies, animals, or foods.\n- **Speed Snaps**: Increase the difficulty by speeding up the snapping process.\n- **Team Play**: Divide into teams and have one team member be the snapper while the rest try to guess.\n\n\"Snaps\" is a great game for parties, road trips, or any occasion where you want a fun, engaging activity!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
